1544
01:51:28,851 --> 01:51:30,041
Không sao đâu, Cogsworth.

1545
01:51:30,244 --> 01:51:31,290
Tôi không thể…

1546
01:51:31,744 --> 01:51:32,787
Lumière,

1547
01:51:33,386 --> 01:51:34,488
