Ông Potts!

1569
01:56:06,887 --> 01:56:07,688
Beatrice!

1570
01:56:07,888 --> 01:56:08,931
Tôi nhớ ra rồi!

1571
01:56:09,188 --> 01:56:10,231
Tôi nhớ ra rồi!

1572
